{"text_id":137185,"tokens":["Title",":"," Relaxation"," Dynamics"," in"," Fluids"," of"," Plate","like"," Coll","oidal"," Particles","\n\n","Abstract",":"," In"," this"," study",","," we"," investigate"," the"," relaxation"," dynamics"," in"," fluids"," composed"," of"," plate","like"," colloidal"," particles",","," addressing"," the"," complex"," interplay"," between"," particle"," shape"," and"," fluid"," behavior","."," The"," motivation"," for"," our"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," to"," understand"," the"," fundamental"," mechanisms"," governing"," the"," relaxation"," processes"," in"," anisotropic"," colloidal"," systems",","," which"," are"," pivotal"," for"," applications"," in"," material"," science"," and"," industrial"," formulations","."," We"," aim"," to"," elucidate"," how"," the"," unique"," geometry"," of"," plate","like"," particles"," influences"," the"," temporal"," evolution"," of"," structural"," and"," dynamical"," properties"," in"," colloidal"," suspensions","."," Utilizing"," a"," combination"," of"," advanced"," experimental"," techniques"," and"," computational"," simulations",","," we"," systematically"," analyze"," the"," relaxation"," times","cales"," and"," the"," corresponding"," structural"," rearrange","ments","."," Our"," methodology"," includes"," dynamic"," light"," scattering"," to"," probe"," the"," temporal"," correlation"," functions"," and"," molecular"," dynamics"," simulations"," to"," capture"," the"," microscopic"," interactions"," and"," trajectories"," of"," the"," particles","."," We"," also"," employ"," theoretical"," models"," to"," interpret"," the"," experimental"," and"," simulation"," data",","," providing"," a"," comprehensive"," framework"," for"," understanding"," the"," relaxation"," phenomena","."," Our"," findings"," reveal"," distinct"," relaxation"," behaviors"," that"," are"," strongly"," dependent"," on"," particle"," concentration"," and"," aspect"," ratio",","," offering"," new"," insights"," into"," the"," design"," and"," control"," of"," colloidal"," systems"," with"," tailored"," dynamic"," properties","."," This"," work"," contributes"," to"," the"," broader"," understanding"," of"," anisotropic"," colloidal"," dynamics"," and"," p","aves"," the"," way"," for"," future"," explorations"," in"," complex"," fluid"," systems","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4o","label":1}